				<text>You promise the Trash Eater additional scrap for work and a home onboard a non-destroyed ship. After beaming aboard, they consume the Flak Cannon, chuckling to themselves.</text>
				<crewMember amount="1" class="trash_eater" all_skills="1">Trash Eater</crewMember>
				<achievement silent="false">ACH_TCC_TRASH_EATER</achievement>
			</event>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<text>Spend some extra time salvaging.</text>
				<event>
					<text>You instead spend some extra time salvaging and beam away without looking back.
						The wounded Trash Eater watches you beam away, who knows if it will live or die floating forever, lost in space wreckage. How rude. 
