		<!--<event name="SCRAPPER_ENCOUNTER_CRUISER"/>-->
	</loadEventList>
</event>


<event name="SCRAPPER_ENCOUNTER_SHOP">
	<text>A scrapper vessel is in this sector. It's broadcasting a signal simply asking for scrap. Perhaps they mean to trade?</text>
	<ship load="SCRAPPER_SHOP" hostile="false" />
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Attack them!</text>
		<event>
			<text>"3XCUSE M3!?!"</text>
			<text>It seems a boarding party has entered your ship. Maybe they had a super shield bypass?</text>
			<ship hostile="true"/>
			<boarders min="2" max="2" class="scrapper_soldier" />
			<boarders min="1" max="1" class="scrapper_medic" />
			<boarders min="1" max="1" class="scrapper_heavy" />
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK" />
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Hail them and see if they want scrap.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"W3 NEED SCRAP!" </text>
			<store>SCRAPPER_NORMAL_STORE</store>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice req="LIST_CREW_SCRAPPER" blue="true" hidden="true">
		<text>Your scrapper waves his hands and sends a signal to the scrapper ship; "C0UPON COD3!!!" They type in a short code and you notice the store prices drop!</text>
		<event>
			<text>"W3 NEED SCRAP!" </text>
			<store>SCRAPPER_NORMAL_STORE_DISCOUNT</store>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="SCRAPPER_ENCOUNTER_BOMBER">
	<text>A scrapper vessel is in this sector. It gives you no warning before powering it's weapons. It hails you, screaming something about scrap.</text>
	<ship load="SCRAPPER_BOMBER" hostile="true" />
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK" />
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="SCRAPPER_ENCOUNTER_CRUISER">
	<text>A scrapper vessel is in this sector. It gives you no warning before powering it's weapons. It hails you, screaming something about scrap.</text>
	<ship load="SCRAPPER_CRUISER" hostile="true" />
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK" />
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="SCRAPPER_ENCOUNTER_SUPPORT">
	<text>A scrapper support ship is in this sector. It seems to not notice you, or it does and it does not care.</text>
	<ship load="SCRAPPER_SUPPORT" hostile="false"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Attack the ship before it gets any bright ideas.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The ship powers up it's weapons.</text>
			<ship hostile="true"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK" />
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice req="LIST_CREW_SCRAPPER" blue="true" hidden="true">
		<text>Consult your scrapper.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Your scrapper advises you that the support ship seems to be lost. It is supposed to be with others, as part of a fleet, but this one is alone. They may need help but may find themselves unable to ask. 
			Your scrapper tells you that it would be good to hail them, as scrappers typically only care about 1 thing and are generally not overly hostile to aliens or humans.</text>
			<choice hidden="true" blue="true">
				<text>Hail the scrapper support ship and offer assistance.</text>
				<event>
					<text>The Scrapper captain responds to you with a bit of a flustered tone, "HAPPY T0 S33 FL3SHY C@PTA!N WE ARE IN NEED 0F R3PA!RS!! C@N Y0U SPARE SCR@P!!???"
				It seems that the scrapper does indeed only have 1 thing on its mind.</text>
					<choice>
						<text>Transfer some scrap to help facilitate their repairs.</text>
						<event>
							<text>You send over the scrap...</text>
							<item_modify> 
								<item type="scrap" min="-35" max="-35"/>
							</item_modify>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Continue...</text>
								<event load="SCRAPPER_ENCOUNTER_SUPPORT_CHEK"/>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice req="LIST_CREW_SCRAPPER" blue="true">
						<text>Get your Scrapper to transfer some scrap to help facilitate their repairs.</text>
						<event>
							<text>You send over the scrap...</text>
							<item_modify> 
								<item type="scrap" min="-35" max="-35"/>
							</item_modify>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Continue...</text>
								<event>
									<text>"TH@NK Y0U CAPT@IN! W3 C@N OP3RATE 0UR ENGINES AGAIN!! TAKE FANCY M@CHINE WE F!ND"</text>
									<augment name="CREW_UPGRADER" />
								</event>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice>
						<text>It could be a trap, leave.</text>
						<event>
							<text>You pull away from the Scrapper ship and it makes no move to stop you.</text>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Order your crew to prepare for battle!</text>
					<event>
						<text>You power up your weapons.</text>
						<ship hostile="true"/>
						<choice hidden="true">
							<text>Continue...</text>
							<event load="COMBAT_CHECK" />
						</choice>
					</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Leave them alone.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Leave them alone.</text>
		<event/>
	</choice>
</event>

<eventList name="SCRAPPER_ENCOUNTER_SUPPORT_CHEK">
	<event>
		<text>"TH@NK Y0U CAPT@IN! W3 C@N OP3RATE 0UR ENGINES AGAIN!! TAKE FANCY M@CHINE WE F!ND"</text>
		<augment name="CREW_UPGRADER" />
	</event>
	<event>
